data.description: Step into this inviting abode featuring hardwood flooring in the family room, lending warmth and elegance to the interior. The kitchen boasts white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops, creating a sleek and modern culinary space. With a dedicated laundry room, brushed nickel hardware, and plush carpeting in the bedrooms, comfort and convenience abound throughout.    Outside, a spacious front porch beckons for relaxation and gatherings on this expansive lot. Conveniently located just minutes from both Midtown and downtown Atlanta, this property offers the perfect blend of tranquility and urban accessibility.    Don't miss your chance to make this charming residence your own retreat in the heart of the city. Schedule a viewing today and discover the ideal balance of comfort and convenience.
